blog.description:
A blog providing writers on tumblr opportunities for playing with new ideas.  No obligations, no requirements, just a weekly topic to spark the imagination and bring more love to text posts.
Reblogs welcome!  Please tag your reblogs and stories with #SFWC.  Send the link to have your story indexed here.
Got a prompt idea?  Send it!  Click on "Submit a Prompt Idea."  SFWC can always use new prompts, and it's open to everyone.

summary: Someone out there uploaded a rare hour long documentary on the filming of 'Empire Strikes Back' from 1980. Apparently the...
caption:
Someone out there uploaded a rare hour long documentary on the filming of ‘Empire Strikes Back’ from 1980. Apparently the uploader “…got ahold of a DVD copy of the documentary that a man in France made after winning a reel copy of the film at an auction.”
….
“There are great interviews with Mark Hamill, Carrie Fisher and Harrison Ford, but it’s the discussions with director Irvin Kershner and Gary Kurtz that really make this a wonderful find. Kershner himself says several times that this isn’t a science fiction movie, but a fairytale.” (Source)
